CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 15, 1957, pg. 24 reads: "Clarinet Trio - William Brim, Robert Niklos and Jerome Jackson compose a clarinet trio which participated in the Schenley High School Variety Show held recently in the school auditorium. The boys are also members of the school's marching band. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of clarinet trio William Brim, Robert Niklos, and Jerome Jackson, posed playing clarinets in hallway of Schenley High School for variety show
